original_title: The Jubilee Pudding: 70 Years in the Baking
overview: In the year Queen Elizabeth marks her 70th on the throne, Fortnum & Mason has challenged home bakers to create a tart, cake, or pudding to honor her legacy. Seven judges headed by Dame Mary Berry invite the final five bakers to London where over one extraordinary day they bake their cakes, tarts, and trifles â€“ hoping it will be the winning recipe.
title: The Jubilee Pudding: 70 Years in the Baking
